| Area | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| **Security headers** | None set | Added `helmet()` middleware |
| **Info leakage** | `X-Powered-By` header exposed | Disabled with `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| **DoS protection** | No rate limiting | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **Body parsing** | No size limit | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| **Input validation** | No query param validation | Allowlist check on `/users` query params |
| **Error handling** | No global handler; stack traces leak | Added 404 handler + global error middleware that hides internals in production |
